observations.recommendation:
We recommended that the Municipal Mayor require the MPDO and Municipal Engineer to:
•submit the list of all ongoing government PPAs and those that are to be implemented during the year to the Office of the Auditor at the beginning of the year;
•inform the Auditor within 10 days after the award of the infrastructure project or before the start of the program/activity that the appropriate project signboards and/or public notices were already posted for validation;
•submit the monthly monitoring report as current as possible and updated;and
•ensure the inclusion of all necessary information on project signboards in compliance with the above-cited circular.
